A man who was once severely obese has shed 390lbs and is now running half marathons.

Brian Flemming, from Canton, Michigan, has undergone a dramatic transformation since 2012, when he weighed 625lbs.

The 32-year-old completed his first half-marathon on July 28, 2013, and is currently gearing up for the Detroit Free Press Half Marathon on Sunday.

