'She told me that I was wasting my life and that I should be ashamed that I was throwing it away when there are so many people out there who are fighting to stay alive,' Mr Flemming wrote.

'My future is a lot gloomier. I'm trying to make the brightest future I can, and... you're dragging yourself down,' Ms Eastham told CNN she recalls thinking.

On October 13, 2012, he made the decision to quit drinking cold-turkey, and drastically change his diet.

